Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.16,0:05:51.41,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\1c&H99B9BB&\fs15\frz2.001\move(842,48,801,48,35,5249)}你\N不\N想\N一\N起\N闖\N進
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.16,0:05:51.41,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\1c&H99B9BB&\fs15\move(832,48,794,48,0,5249)}這\N個\N世\N界\N冒\N險\N嗎\N！？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.05,0:05:46.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我的建議只有一個
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.86,0:05:49.91,Default,,0,0,0,,一動不動地 安靜地守望學生吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.44,0:05:51.56,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣就可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.25,0:05:54.82,Default,,0,0,0,,第一天不需要做什麼太難的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.70,0:05:59.18,Default,,0,0,0,,到處走動可能也只是打擾到他們而已
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.73,0:06:00.88,Default,,0,0,0,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.38,0:06:03.14,Default,,0,0,0,,一動不動…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.65,0:06:04.74,Default,,0,0,0,,安靜…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.42,0:06:06.73,Default,,0,0,0,,守望他們…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.10,0:06:16.94,Default,,0,0,0,,平時就那麼堂堂正正的偷懶…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.91,0:06:20.27,Default,,0,0,0,,難道社長是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.76,0:06:23.25,Default,,0,0,0,,不良少年嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.30,0:06:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.76,0:06:31.65,Default,,0,0,0,,但這兩位似乎有在認真畫畫呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.18,0:06:38.26,Default,,0,0,0,,根據資料 內卷昴同學似乎是得過獎的優秀社員
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.50,0:06:45.03,Default,,0,0,0,,那投入的表情 確實就連我這外行人也明白
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.59,0:06:48.87,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了 有認真的同學
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.35,0:06:49.85,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.04,0:06:54.22,Default,,0,0,0,,那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.42,0:06:56.07,Default,,0,0,0,,前陣子在書局拿到的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.77,0:06:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,不要在社辦放這種東西啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.03,0:07:02.34,Default,,0,0,0,,不行 畢竟是正值這個時期的男生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.82,0:07:06.10,Default,,0,0,0,,不能憑一張動畫泳衣女孩就認定他是變態
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.23,0:07:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,,也要向老師介紹一下呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.30,0:07:11.70,Default,,0,0,0,,這位是我的老婆
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.94,0:07:13.37,Default,,0,0,0,,是變態呀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.63,0:07:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,不良少年跟變態
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.73,0:07:20.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我能堅持下去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.00,0:07:22.97,Default,,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.14,0:07:26.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我去呼吸下新鮮空氣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.07,0:07:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,感覺她沒什麼精神呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.19,0:07:32.45,Default,,0,0,0,,都怪內卷同學說了些不該說的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.50,0:07:35.02,Default,,0,0,0,,但我都跟平時一樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.02,0:07:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,快點發覺你平時就很奇怪這件事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.50,0:07:39.94,Default,,0,0,0,,先不說這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.99,0:07:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,老師不在的話會很麻煩呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.12,0:07:43.74,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣就不能繼續下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.63,0:07:48.51,Default,,0,0,0,,那就讓社長留住她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.97,0:07:49.67,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼做？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.10,0:07:51.57,Default,,0,0,0,,閒話家常作戰
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.55,0:07:59.03,Default,,0,0,0,,社長 請你起來 社長
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.67,0:08:01.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我們需要社長的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.53,0:08:03.77,Default,,0,0,0,,再讓我睡一個小時
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.00,0:08:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我真是沒用 這點小事就失去信心了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.95,0:08:16.74,Default,,0,0,0,,老師 差不多了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.76,0:08:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,你頭上那個是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.27,0:08:22.23,Default,,0,0,0,,請不要在意細節
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.18,0:08:28.55,Default,,0,0,0,,那就看你的了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.66,0:08:30.23,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.57,0:08:32.06,Default,,0,0,0,,閒話家常作戰就是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.67,0:08:36.19,Default,,0,0,0,,社長隨便瞎扯些話題 吸引老師的注意就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.74,0:08:40.36,Default,,0,0,0,,天氣真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.34,0:08:44.35,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊 這天氣最適合午睡了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.68,0:08:48.32,Default,,0,0,0,,不許睡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.77,0:08:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然他們好像一直不許我在社辦睡覺
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.04,0:08:56.73,Default,,0,0,0,,但我只是做了類似那樣的事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.31,0:08:59.11,Default,,0,0,0,,絕對不代表我在睡午覺
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.54,0:09:00.72,Default,,0,0,0,,是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.64,0:09:05.21,Default,,0,0,0,,像是在睡午覺並不代表真的在睡午覺
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.19,0:09:06.64,BackGround,,0,0,0,,是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.44,0:09:38.74,Default,,0,0,0,,然後 忍不住就把被子給…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.96,0:09:39.74,Default,,0,0,0,,完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.08,0:09:42.48,Default,,0,0,0,,畫好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.62,0:09:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.16,0:09:45.46,Default,,0,0,0,,能給我看看嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.62,0:09:46.32,Default,,0,0,0,,當然
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.52,0:09:49.19,Default,,0,0,0,,好期待啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.56,0:09:51.67,Default,,0,0,0,,兩位會畫出怎樣的畫呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.46,0:10:12.47,Default,,0,0,0,,再次歡迎來到美術社 立花老師
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.27,0:10:15.05,Default,,0,0,0,,這就是驚喜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.37,0:10:23.90,Default,,0,0,0,,你們今天就是一直在畫這個嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.92,0:10:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.96,0:10:31.14,Default,,0,0,0,,一動不動地 安靜地守望學生吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.50,0:10:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,莫非小山老師也知道這個驚喜嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.13,0:10:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 是小山老師提出的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.55,0:10:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,小山老師 謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.90,0:10:46.22,Default,,0,0,0,,那個 小山老師還健在的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.58,0:10:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼請老師用一句話來結尾一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.94,0:10:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,,這個主意不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.18,0:10:55.45,BackGround,,0,0,0,,那個 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.78,0:10:56.02,Default,,0,0,0,,來 麥克風
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.21,0:10:57.26,Default,,0,0,0,,不擅長這種
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.33,0:10:58.44,Default,,0,0,0,,說什麼都可以啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.94,0:11:16.23,Default,,0,0,0,,那個 我、不會輸給前任的…小山老師
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.24,0:11:19.85,Default,,0,0,0,, 我會加油的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.49,0:11:21.71,Default,,0,0,0,,請… 請…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.50,0:11:24.33,Default,,0,0,0,,請多多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.66,0:11:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我又做蠢事了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.25,0:11:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,,老師真可愛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.68,0:11:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,嬌羞萌嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.10,0:11:38.21,Default,,0,0,0,,就這樣我作為美術社顧問的第一天落下了帷幕
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.50,0:11:40.99,Default,,0,0,0,,社員們都是一群好孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.00,0:11:42.87,Default,,0,0,0,,看來今後也會過得很愉快
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.17,0:11:47.17,Default,,0,0,0,,咦？ 好像忘記了什麼事情
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.51,0:11:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,那個老師是真的啊！？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.86,0:11:51.26,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.98,0:11:56.98,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\bord4\fs35\1c&H130D24&\3c&HEFF3EF&\frz344.4\pos(1028,394)}大\N家\N冷\N靜\N點
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.98,0:11:56.98,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\bord4\fs35\1c&H130D24&\3c&HEFF3EF&\frz16.86\pos(514,328)}那\N個\N人\N真\N的\N是\N老\N師
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.98,0:12:01.99,Title,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,450)}可蕾散步
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.39,0:12:42.03,Default,,0,0,0,,妳在做什麼啊 祈禱嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.27,0:12:45.26,Default,,0,0,0,,是在對那個人的弔唁
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.65,0:12:46.33,Default,,0,0,0,,弔唁？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.82,0:12:47.41,Default,,0,0,0,,快看
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.54,0:12:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,他走在陽光下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.14,0:12:53.15,Default,,0,0,0,,那個已經不行了 出局
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.47,0:12:55.47,Default,,0,0,0,,規則如此
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.83,0:13:03.21,Default,,0,0,0,,欸
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.50,0:13:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,妳和姐姐我以前在哪裡見過面吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.25,0:13:10.85,Default,,0,0,0,,是我認錯了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.05,0:13:11.87,Default,,0,0,0,,算了 沒差
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.04,0:13:14.67,Default,,0,0,0,,注意別讓太陽曬到喔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.00,0:13:16.95,Default,,0,0,0,,拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.60,0:13:22.87,Default,,0,0,0,,讓妳久等了 萌香
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.26,0:13:25.35,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼出發吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.63,0:13:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.76,0:13:29.72,Default,,0,0,0,,有乖乖的在等媽媽 妳好棒喔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.48,0:13:32.35,Default,,0,0,0,,萌香晚上想吃什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.13,0:13:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,這個嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.17,0:13:40.65,Default,,0,0,0,,昨天是咖哩 今天做漢堡排吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.90,0:13:41.75,Default,,0,0,0,,泡飯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.70,0:13:41.72,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}※お茶漬け\N\h\h{\fscx80\fscy80}用茶來沖的一種泡飯料理
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.92,0:13:43.67,Default,,0,0,0,,萌香的喜好好古典啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.72,0:13:43.97,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}※渋い\N\h\h{\fscx80\fscy80}指茶的苦味。另外形容人則是指有滄桑的感覺。海賊王裡的黃猿就屬於這一類
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.75,0:13:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了？ 萌香
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.87,0:13:49.45,Default,,0,0,0,,媽媽出局了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.92,0:13:50.11,Default,,0,0,0,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.89,0:13:56.95,Default,,0,0,0,,原來是不可以走出陰影地帶啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.10,0:13:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 規則如此
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.93,0:14:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼媽媽也該多多注意
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.55,0:14:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.78,0:14:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,對了 萌香給爺爺的禮物有準備好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.77,0:14:07.99,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.47,0:14:09.51,Default,,0,0,0,,圓石
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.44,0:14:11.34,Default,,0,0,0,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.31,0:14:13.94,Default,,0,0,0,,還有爺爺的畫像
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.25,0:14:17.05,Default,,0,0,0,,畫得真好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.66,0:14:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,爺爺一定會高興的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.30,0:14:22.61,Default,,0,0,0,,話說萌香畫得真是不錯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.08,0:14:24.65,Default,,0,0,0,,長大了會成為畫家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.08,0:14:26.97,Default,,0,0,0,,美實社
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.19,0:14:30.63,Default,,0,0,0,,萌香長大了要去美實社
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.27,0:14:32.59,Default,,0,0,0,,美實社？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.58,0:14:35.65,Default,,0,0,0,,是美術社啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.69,0:14:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.14,0:14:37.93,Default,,0,0,0,,話說起來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.93,0:14:42.53,Default,,0,0,0,,爺爺不久前還當過美術社的老師
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.41,0:14:44.95,Default,,0,0,0,,爺爺是美術社的？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.31,0:14:46.76,Default,,0,0,0,,讓爺爺來教教妳吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.67,0:14:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.59,0:14:50.05,Default,,0,0,0,,萌香
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.65,0:14:52.39,Default,,0,0,0,,出局了～
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.72,0:15:15.72,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\bord4\fs40\1c&H130D24&\3c&HEFF3EF&\frz288.8\pos(90,250)}…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.72,0:15:15.72,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\bord4\fs40\1c&H130D24&\3c&HEFF3EF&\frz13.58\pos(70,288)}妳\N在\N搞\N什\N麼\N？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.72,0:15:15.72,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\bord4\fs40\1c&H130D24&\3c&HEFF3EF&\pos(998,432)\frz344.6}社
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.72,0:15:15.72,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\bord4\fs40\1c&H130D24&\3c&HEFF3EF&\frz251.5\pos(1020,480)}…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.72,0:15:15.72,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\bord4\fs40\1c&H130D24&\3c&HEFF3EF&\pos(838,384)\frz350.6}社\N長\N{\fsp-10}！？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.72,0:15:20.75,Title,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,450)}一點點地，慢慢地
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.64,0:15:31.06,Default,,0,0,0,,洗完澡後來突襲的睡魔為什麼這麼強大
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.21,0:15:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,內卷同學真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.51,0:15:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,米粒黏在臉上了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.87,0:15:47.95,Default,,0,0,0,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.95,0:15:49.07,Default,,0,0,0,,幫我拿下來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.07,0:15:50.51,Default,,0,0,0,,真是拿你沒轍
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.54,0:16:03.76,BackGround,,0,0,0,,瑞希～
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.33,0:16:05.19,BackGround,,0,0,0,,喂～
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.42,0:16:07.60,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼啦～
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.78,0:16:08.55,BackGround,,0,0,0,,快起來 瑞希
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.94,0:16:14.05,Default,,0,0,0,,媽媽！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.05,0:16:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,終於醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.40,0:16:17.56,Default,,0,0,0,,進來前先敲門啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.56,0:16:19.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我敲過了 可是妳睡著了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.75,0:16:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,,不會吧 現在幾點？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.76,0:16:22.73,Default,,0,0,0,,八點半
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.73,0:16:25.97,Default,,0,0,0,,好險好險 作業還沒做
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.73,0:16:29.10,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉 有什麼事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.10,0:16:30.15,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 差點忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.99,0:16:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,有妳的電話 內卷同學打的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.76,0:16:38.46,Default,,0,0,0,,喂喂 內卷同學
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.46,0:16:40.73,BackGround,,0,0,0,,抱歉 沒想到妳竟然已經睡了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.47,0:16:44.71,Default,,0,0,0,,腦袋有點迷迷糊糊的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.21,0:16:48.61,Default,,0,0,0,,對了 這個時間打電話來有什麼事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.66,0:16:50.18,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.06,0:16:53.65,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 哎 還沒…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.09,0:16:56.06,Default,,0,0,0,,等我一下 內卷同學
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.83,0:16:58.53,Default,,0,0,0,,給我出去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.37,0:17:00.91,Default,,0,0,0,,不用在意我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.91,0:17:01.73,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼不在意啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.16,0:17:05.73,Default,,0,0,0,,你們還沒交換號碼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.73,0:17:07.01,Default,,0,0,0,,別管啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.71,0:17:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,,要是那麼簡單就能問到 我就不用這麼辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.15,0:17:15.31,Default,,0,0,0,,是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.41,0:17:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,,喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.74,0:17:19.37,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 已經可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.02,0:17:20.70,Default,,0,0,0,,然後…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.61,0:17:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,作業的影本怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.01,0:17:28.82,BackGround,,0,0,0,,其實我剛發現書包裡裝的是宇佐美同學的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.82,0:17:30.17,Default,,0,0,0,,哎 不會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.18,0:17:33.53,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 還真的不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.53,0:17:37.84,Default,,0,0,0,,恐怕是因為可蕾特同學今天玩的那個魔術秀吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.02,0:17:40.95,Default,,0,0,0,,今天一直都在玩那個呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.95,0:17:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,然後就是 這張紙將會消失在異次元
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.58,0:17:49.13,Default,,0,0,0,,一二 看招
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.03,0:17:56.68,Default,,0,0,0,,接… 接著進行下一個魔術
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.68,0:17:59.01,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 把這個收拾乾淨後再說
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.13,0:18:01.35,Default,,0,0,0,,真讓人頭痛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.35,0:18:02.39,BackGround,,0,0,0,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.13,0:18:06.11,BackGround,,0,0,0,,我現在就把妳的那份拿去妳家
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.59,0:18:10.82,Default,,0,0,0,,哎 現在就來嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.82,0:18:12.28,BackGround,,0,0,0,,嗯 現在就去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.28,0:18:14.47,Default,,0,0,0,,那、那麼突然…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.97,0:18:16.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我還沒做好準備…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.03,0:18:18.64,BackGround,,0,0,0,,準備？ 只是把影本拿給妳而已啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.24,0:18:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,話雖如此
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.16,0:18:22.46,BackGround,,0,0,0,,那等會見
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.79,0:18:24.72,Default,,0,0,0,,等會見
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.24,0:18:32.61,BackGround,,0,0,0,,那麼接下來是明天的天氣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.29,0:18:37.47,BackGround,,0,0,0,,從北部往南受到高氣壓的影響 全國都是晴天
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.24,0:18:35.71,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.64,0:18:40.54,Default,,0,0,0,,等一下瑞希
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.54,0:18:42.76,Default,,0,0,0,,妳要出門嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.45,0:18:45.11,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有啊 為什麼這麼問
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.89,0:18:47.41,Default,,0,0,0,,那幹嘛要穿成這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.67,0:18:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,很奇怪嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.36,0:18:51.17,Default,,0,0,0,,也不是說奇怪 只是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.90,0:18:54.16,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 難道是為了內卷同學嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.61,0:18:59.01,Default,,0,0,0,,不是 這是那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.63,0:19:02.91,Default,,0,0,0,,才不是為了想讓他看才穿成這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.49,0:19:06.21,Default,,0,0,0,,只是為了保持自己的形象
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.61,0:19:09.84,Default,,0,0,0,,喔 說來就來了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.16,0:19:11.59,Default,,0,0,0,,那我就先…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.59,0:19:12.25,Default,,0,0,0,,瑞希
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.57,0:19:14.61,Default,,0,0,0,,很漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.34,0:19:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,,一點都不奇怪喔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.09,0:19:22.37,Default,,0,0,0,,謝了 媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.89,0:19:31.44,Default,,0,0,0,,打擾了 晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.52,0:19:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,幹嘛這麼見外
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.04,0:19:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,和平常一樣就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.75,0:19:37.84,Default,,0,0,0,,因為…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.86,0:19:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,,盯…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.55,0:19:44.27,Default,,0,0,0,,請不要介意
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.27,0:19:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,會介意的啊！！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.21,0:19:48.13,Default,,0,0,0,,去外面說吧 去外面
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.56,0:19:51.57,Default,,0,0,0,,真是一點都大意不得
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.42,0:19:54.57,Default,,0,0,0,,妳的作業影本
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.57,0:19:56.06,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.39,0:19:58.93,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉呢 這麼晚的時間還麻煩你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.93,0:20:02.02,Default,,0,0,0,,不用在意 我才是該抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.02,0:20:03.77,Default,,0,0,0,,在妳睡著的時候吵醒妳
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.59,0:20:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,這個話題就不要提了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.59,0:20:08.63,Default,,0,0,0,,沒想到這麼早就睡了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.63,0:20:12.18,Default,,0,0,0,,不要說了 別把我當成懶散角色啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.18,0:20:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,洗完澡後就有點迷迷糊糊的 並不是我很懶散啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.80,0:20:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,有在聽嗎 內卷同學？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.81,0:20:23.35,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 原來是這樣 剛洗過澡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.11,0:20:27.25,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了 不行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.25,0:20:29.18,Default,,0,0,0,,不 不是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.18,0:20:33.13,Default,,0,0,0,,只是從剛才就覺得宇佐美同學身上有股香味
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.02,0:20:39.01,Default,,0,0,0,,太狡猾了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.53,0:20:42.79,Default,,0,0,0,,這麼輕易就說出這種話
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.44,0:20:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,,那我就先回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.25,0:20:51.85,Default,,0,0,0,,等一下 內卷同學
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.94,0:20:55.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我有個提議
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.44,0:20:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,有帶手機嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.80,0:21:01.26,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 是有帶了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.64,0:21:03.73,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼 那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.69,0:21:08.45,Default,,0,0,0,,剛才突然想到了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.45,0:21:12.67,Default,,0,0,0,,為了今後遇到這種事能更有效率的聯絡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.99,0:21:15.68,Default,,0,0,0,,那個… 那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.09,0:21:24.91,Default,,0,0,0,,請和我交換一下手機號碼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.91,0:21:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.94,0:21:26.36,BackGround,,0,0,0,,這當然不是強迫你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.36,0:21:28.53,BackGround,,0,0,0,,而且我也清楚內卷同學覺得這種事情很麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.53,0:21:30.83,BackGround,,0,0,0,,但是知道對方的號碼的話絕對會很方便…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.80,0:21:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,可以嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.20,0:21:34.81,Default,,0,0,0,,當然了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.41,0:21:42.51,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.51,0:21:43.87,Default,,0,0,0,,不用客氣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.64,0:21:48.14,Default,,0,0,0,,那、那今天就打擾了…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.14,0:21:50.31,Default,,0,0,0,,幹嘛又這麼見外
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.56,0:21:52.51,Default,,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.16,0:21:57.11,Default,,0,0,0,,請不要介意
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.11,0:21:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,都說了會介意啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.44,0:22:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的 媽媽
